 I am also confident in my ability for verbal description, as I am a practiced
 public speaker.
 I have experience through lectures and conference presentations, and additional
ly as a commentator for a TV broadcast of local soccer games.
 With an appropriate three-pronged description of all concepts, I believe
 students will have a much easier time latching on to something and learning
 the underlying material.
